// Letter variant. Compile: typst compile --font-path fonts example-letter.typ
#import "lokta.typ": *

#show: lokta-letter.with(
  sender: ("The Lokta Office", "Paper on Screen"),
  recipient: ("A. Reader", "Everywhere"),
  date: "1 April 2026",
  subject: "On the choice of stock",
  sign: "The Lokta Office",
)

Thank you for asking which stock to set. Paper is the default and reads warm.
Bone is the cooler near-white when cream is too much. Ink and Indigo carry the
dark rooms. Every text role clears AA on each, so the choice is yours to make on
feel alone.
